IN THE HIGH COURT OF PUNJAB AND HARYANA AT CHANDIGARH RSA No. 764 of 1990 (O&M) Date of decision: March 21, 2013 Pepsu Road Transport Corporation ...Appellant Versus Harmohinder Singh ...Respondent CORAM:- HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE A.N. JINDAL Present: None. A.N. JINDAL, J.

(Oral)

Case has been called twice since morning but none has put in appearance on behalf of the parties. It appears that the appellant is not interested in pursuing the present appeal. Dismissed for want of prosecution. March 21, 2013 (A.N. JINDAL) 'sp' JUDGE
